U7 chit8-kang, kok-hau7-a2 pang3-oh8 tng2-kau3 chhu3, chu-pau khng3--leh, to7 khi3 chhan5-piN e5 chhai3-hng5 khoaN3 a-pa3 gia5 ti5-thau5 teh kut8 chhai3-kou2.
SoaN-piN jit8-thau5 tng beh loh8-soaN, thin-sek tauh8-tauh8-a2 am3--loh8-lai5, chhan5--nih e5 chhek-chiau2-a2 toa7-tin7 toa7-tin7 poe-khi3 hioh ti7 tek-pho7 lai7, goa2 kap a-pa3 ti7 chhai3-hng5 thoaN2-chhau2, peng2-thou5......na2 cho3 na2 khai-kang2. A-pa3 hiong5-hiong5 ka7 goa2 kho2 chit8-e5 bun7-te5: “A-me-a2, tek-a2 ui3 toeh lai5--e5?” Goa2 siuN7-siuN7--leh, in3 kong2: “ThiN-te7 seN-seng5--e5-lah!” Che si7 a-kong ka3--e5, siaN2-mih tai7-chi3 na7 chhoe7 bo5 tap-an3, to7-si “thiN-te7 seN-seng5--e5”.
A-pa3 haiN3-thau5, ka7 goa2 ka3-si7 chit8-khun3, chiah kong2: “Si7 ui3 Tek-kok lai5--e5-lah, ‘tek’ to7-si7 Tek-kok e5 ‘tek’, li2 thak8-chu long2 bo5 thak8 thiat-te2!” ThiaN-liau2, goa2 chiok khim-phoe3 a-pa3--e5, a-pa3 sui-bong2 m7-bat ji7, m7-koh hak8-bun7 u7-kau3 ho2--e5. Sun7 a-pa3 e5 oe7-boe2, goa2 ma7 liau2-kai2 ‘bi2’ si7 an2-choaN2 kio3-cho3 ‘bi2’ ---- si7 ui3 Bi2-kok lai5--e5 a. A-pa3 thiaN kah chin moa2-i3, o-lo2 kong2 goa2 cheng3-keng si7 in kiaN2.
Chin che7 ni5 liau2-au7, koh siuN7-tioh8 a-pa3 e5『腦筋急轉彎』, goa2 koh e7 chhio3 kah oai-io--khi3, goa2 teh siuN7, ka-ti7 e7 kui-kang “siuN7-khang siuN7-phang7” “piN3-kui2 piN3-koai3”, hoan7-se3 si7 cheng2-tioh8 goan2 a-pa3!
(TGB Thong-sin3 te7 43 ki5, 2003 ni5 4 goeh8)
